[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……よし。\nこれで、目的の鉱石は採取できた",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "レジナさん、協力してくれてありがとう。\n……姉さんも",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "レジナ、私からもありがとう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "レジナ",
		"romanized_name": "Regina",
		"model_path_hash": "6530292426083289682",
		"text": "あっはは、力になれたならよかったよ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5764066045850619995",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "レジナ",
		"romanized_name": "Regina",
		"model_path_hash": "6530292426083289682",
		"text": "で、これから二人はどうする予定？\n紀行文のための旅を続けるの？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5764066045850619995",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "実は、このハイネ州が旅の最後の目的地だったの。\nこの後は王都州に戻る予定よ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "レジナ",
		"romanized_name": "Regina",
		"model_path_hash": "6530292426083289682",
		"text": "そっか。気を付けて帰るんだよ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5764066045850619995",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "レジナ、また会いましょう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……うん。またね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "私はこれから、これまでの旅の内容をまとめて\n本にする作業を進めるわ……ミルカはどうするの？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……採取したものを整理するわ。\n珍しいものも手に入ったから、色々と見てみる",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "そう、分かった。\nアトリエに行くのよね。気を付けて",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "うん……またね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……よし、この鉱石があれば――",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "322297020958821866",
		"text": "お邪魔しまーす……って、あ！　ミルカ！\n帰って来てたんだね！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "90362210238560528",
		"text": "ミルカさん！　お帰りなさい！\nユリエさんとの旅は、どうでしたか？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……悪くなかった。\n色々と、いい素材も手に入ったし",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "あなたたちは、水遊び楽しめた？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "322297020958821866",
		"text": "ちょー楽しかったよ！\n今度は絶対、ミルカも一緒に遊ぼうね！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……うん",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "90362210238560528",
		"text": "ところでミルカさん。\nこんなにたくさんの素材、何に使うんですか？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "90362210238560528",
		"text": "見たところ、何か調合の準備中かなって……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……それなんだけど――",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "私、調合したいものがあるの。\nシャル、シャリー……手伝ってくれないかしら",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]